<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="progressive-adj">progressive <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /prə'ɡresɪv/    美 /prə'ɡresɪv/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>进步的；先进的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>progressive schools 
先进的学校</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>发展中的；(疾病) 逐渐恶化的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>progressive memory loss 
逐渐失忆</p></div></div>